{"tid":2267924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍尼日利亞救出被脅持公民","createTime":"2020-11-02T12:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T17:30:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"90d47198146673e88bfbf171f18302be02238bb5","tid":2267924,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201102/5CF454ADD5EA3BRWAJN5C46R3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201102%2F5CF454ADD5EA3BRWAJN5C46R3M%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=4ad50c1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201102%2F5CF454ADD5EA3BRWAJN5C46R3M%2F&h=6c6fddb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201102/5CF454ADD5EA3BRWAJN5C46R3M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美軍尼日利亞救出被脅持公民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oH4fdKJtssjcnjsYdZbq9DNrz-w=/1000x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7MJ27X3D2RH6RGSRXOWRPK4QDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoH4fdKJtssjcnjsYdZbq9DNrz-w%3D%2F1000x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7MJ27X3D2RH6RGSRXOWRPK4QDU.jpg&h=237a1ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沃爾頓<br />\n<br />\n.......................................，過程中美方沒有傷亡，人質安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普讚「重大勝利」<br />\n<br />\n27歲的沃爾頓（Philipe Walton）上周初在尼日爾南部距離尼日利亞邊境約10公里的馬薩拉塔村家中，被六名持AK-47自動步槍的匪徒闖入搜掠和擄到尼日利亞。據報匪徒是富拉尼人，說豪薩語和少許英語，曾致電沃爾頓的父親要求贖金。沃爾頓的父親指自己住在尼日爾30年，而兒子則在兩年前開始與妻女住在該村。沃爾頓在當地以畜牧和種植維生。<br />\n<br />\n國防部指營救行動在上周五晚上進行，形容參與行動的美軍是「英勇的戰士」。總統特朗普亦讚揚「美國特種部隊的精英取得重大勝利」，又指「這是該做的事，因為他們在挑釁美國人」。據報數名綁匪在行動中被殺。<br />\n<br />\n消息指參與行動的是「海豹」特種部隊第六隊。有美國官員透露，沒有確實證據顯示事件與恐怖主義有關，「更傾向是勒索贖金」，不過美國政府擔心人質或會被交予其他恐怖組織，或演變成長期綁架。美國當局指家人沒有支付贖金。尼日爾外交消息指，沃爾頓現暫居在美國大使官邸。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社"},{"pid":"67da7efa7eb1f302470376a10a581278f9ed2abc","tid":2267924,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe8360648a42a5b6faeffb93fc7196e030bfde1","tid":2267924,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"藍定紅?"},{"pid":"13f791c6d5765d14468c9fb2921fca067e295e22","tid":2267924,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"又有電影題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67057ad9faafebfed97175d52b6ae9f5aaad0a28","tid":2267924,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b58c704bf05d72d25019481862a91d860166fde","tid":2267924,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 